  "title": "High-resolution spatially-resolved proteome mapping using automated, sacrificial liquid-mediated sample transfer from laser microdissection to nanodroplet sample preparation",
  "additionalAttributes": [],
  "projectDescription": "Method development for high-resolution spatially-resolved proteome mapping of tissue heterogeneity. Laser microdissection was coupled with nanodroplet sample preparation and ultrasensitive LC-MS.",
